file_content.text: Clearing Zone Twelve would remove key Imperial holding.
Imperials will never take Corellia, not while we stand.
Imperials want to collapse our tunnels. Whole septs could die.
Have some news about the escape pod. You and Drizan should hear.
Fewer droids, we can move freely. Help us, we help you.
A defender? Drizan will be glad.
Too many Imperials. Where's our help?
